   triggering SIGSEGV.
   
   The root cause manifestes in two distinct scenarios within
   `md2html/md2html.c` and `md4c/render_html.c`:
   1. **Minimal fix**: Adding a capacity check before buffer writes
   2. **Root-cause fix**: Revising buffer growth logic to properly handle edge
   cases
   
